  "title": "Project Manager (Commercial ID Renovation / Interior Fit-Out)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position : Project Manager (Commercial ID Renovation / Interior Fit-Out)</strong></p><p><u>Employment Type</u><br />1. Full-time </p><p><u>Experience</u><br />1. At least 2 years of experience in commercial renovation or construction projects (e.g. F&B, office, retail).</p><p><u>Skill Requirements</u><br />1. Proficient in Microsoft Office (Excel, Word, PowerPoint)<br />2. Basic AutoCAD knowledge is a plus<br />3. Valid driving licence preferred; own vehicle is an advantage.<br />4. Able to work independently and handle site matters</p><p><u>Roles & Responsibilities</u><br />1. Supervise subcontractors before and during renovation works<br />2. Plan and manage renovation schedules<br />3. Prepare quotations and follow up on costs with subcontractors and suppliers<br />4. Coordinate fit-out submissions with Landlord / Building Management<br />5. Conduct site measurement and site survey<br />6. Attend client meetings and handle renovation defects<br />7. Basic design and renovation knowledge required</p><p><u>Language</u><br />1. Fluent in English required for documentation, coordination, and client communication. </p><p><u>Salary</u><br />1. Basic Salary + Allowance + Project Incentive (up to $4,000 to $6,000 per month) (Subject to experience and projects involved)</p><p><u>Application</u><br />1. Please send your detailed resume (including past projects and role) to<br />📧 <u>admin@3plusidesign.com</u></p>",
