    "uen": "201833525H",
    "description": "<p>3+I Design Studio Pte. Ltd. is a Singapore-based interior design firm specializing in commercial and F&amp;B spaces, with a growing presence in residential projects. With a strong emphasis on creativity, functionality, and project delivery, we provide end-to-end interior solutions — from concept development to space planning, 3D visualization, and renovation execution.<br>\n<br>\nOur team is passionate about transforming spaces into practical yet aesthetically refined environments that align with our clients' branding and operational goals. Over the years, we have completed a wide range of office, café, restaurant, and retail design projects across Singapore, gaining a solid reputation for design innovation and client satisfaction.<br>\n<br>\nWe are a collaborative, fast-paced team that values initiative, responsibility, and attention to detail. As we expand, we are looking for creative and committed individuals to join us on our journey.</p>",
